modName: KDS Character Creation with Major Headstart with Coins
summary: This is a cheat save for those of you who want a huge hand at the beginning of the game.
descriptionHtml:
This is a save game set literally just before you choose who your character should be.
Also I have placed 1000 lockpicks and 1.5 million Septim coins on you.

Purchase all, pick all the locks.

Happy hunting :)

To install place this inside the save folder, should be found here:
Documents/MyGames/Skyrim/Saves
author: KDStudios
